<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.9.2">
<l>cintai taṉṉuḷ nīṅkā tirunta tiruvē maruviṉiya</l>
<l>maintā vanta ṇāli mālē cōlai maḻakaḷiṟē</l>
<l>nantā viḷakkiṉ cuṭarē naṟaiyūr niṉṟa nampīyeṉ</l>
<l>entā yinta ḷūrā yaṭiyēṟ kiṟaiyu miraṅkāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Treasure who is never departed from our thoughts, sweet fragrant man,</l>
<l>Māl of lovely cool Āli, young elephant of the jungle,</l>
<l>Light of the unextinguished lamp, noble who stood in Naṟaiyūr,</l>
<l>My father, you of Intaḷūr, do you not pity me, your servant, even a bit?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
